<text top="679" left="90" width="69" height="19" font="6"><b>Agenda</b></text>
<text top="721" left="122" width="146" height="14" font="1">The situation in Croatia</text>
<text top="757" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Further report on the situation of human rights in Croatia pursuant to Security Council resolution 1019 (1995)</text>
